reviews.text:
Very local restaurant. Beef and cashews was far too salty. Supposedly steamed fish didn't taste steamed. Also had choi Sam which was fine. About $240 for two people.
We may give in another go as it's close to home... We'll see.
A small yet comfortable restaurant. Good food, reasonable prices, hospitable services. On the whole, a good restaurant.
Nice Hong Kong way of dinner.
Fave place to eat while I was in HK
Guangdong style fry. Not bad. Worth a try.
